{
  "stem": "9665.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And I'm missing him very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "He was a wonderful, wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I-- and-- and I hope-- and I hope, and I think that his relatives in Amsterdam, or wherever they are, that they will-- will remember him as a wonderful, wonderful human being.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Anyway, the first transaction which we did with Czechoslovakia was thanks to Barend Boers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And all the other one were beautiful-- very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "Our first money we made was with Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "My brother came back, as I said before, the second half of 1946.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And the business was already on the go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And it got to the stage where we imported ten thousands of dozens, or thousands of dozens.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] ten thousands of dozens of stockings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And we were only allowed to make a margin of 20%.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "They were still on coupon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "They called it coupon in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "I don't know what they call it in Holland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "I can't think of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "But anyway, we did OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "We made a living.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "We didn't get a lot out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "Before that happened, my parents and my sister and brother-in-law sent me some shoes from Curacao and sent me some clothing, you know, to make money.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "Because in Curacao, they also had everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "Up to the last day, they had it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "When it came, it went straight to the [NON-ENGLISH], which you know by now what it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a-- a business already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had our reciprocity compensation transaction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what we were missing is-- what we were missing when my brother came?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were missing something which we are more attractive, which was to have a factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we didn't have a factory, so we moved from there to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
